1
00:00:08,840 --> 00:00:10,560
You think you're so pretty, new kid?

2
00:00:13,320 --> 00:00:17,000
You think Tawan accepts your drink
and you're better than everyone else?

3
00:00:18,000 --> 00:00:20,200
You turn your nose up at everyone.

4
00:00:20,880 --> 00:00:22,120
You want a drink?

5
00:00:23,000 --> 00:00:23,720
Here.

6
00:00:25,200 --> 00:00:26,680
I prepared it for you.

7
00:00:27,240 --> 00:00:28,600
But not in a glass.

8
00:00:28,960 --> 00:00:30,520
You'll get the whole bucket.

9
00:00:32,600 --> 00:00:35,240
No. No. Don't do it!

10
00:00:43,880 --> 00:00:44,880
Tawan.

11
00:00:47,880 --> 00:00:49,240
Tawan.

12
00:00:49,640 --> 00:00:51,720
Why did you have to go this far?

13
00:00:52,080 --> 00:00:54,840
I'm sorry. It wasn't meant for you.

14
00:00:54,840 --> 00:00:56,320
It was meant for this new kid.

15
00:00:56,840 --> 00:00:57,920
She just got here.

16
00:00:58,000 --> 00:01:00,360
How could she get this close to you?

17
00:01:00,440 --> 00:01:02,280
I'm the reason, right?

18
00:01:03,520 --> 00:01:05,760
I don't approve of this behavior.

19
00:01:07,360 --> 00:01:09,240
Bullying is contemptible

20
00:01:09,600 --> 00:01:11,280
and unacceptable.

21
00:01:11,560 --> 00:01:12,880
No matter to whom.

22
00:01:15,200 --> 00:01:16,680
It breaks my heart

23
00:01:17,400 --> 00:01:19,640
that I'm not setting a good example.

24
00:01:19,920 --> 00:01:21,680
Tawan, no.

25
00:01:22,000 --> 00:01:23,240
It's not your fault.

26
00:01:23,240 --> 00:01:25,600
You're very good. You've always been good.

27
00:01:25,680 --> 00:01:27,280
It's our fault.

28
00:01:27,280 --> 00:01:28,760
We're really sorry.

29
00:01:28,960 --> 00:01:30,200
-I'm sorry.
-I'm sorry.

30
00:01:32,440 --> 00:01:33,800
Then let this end here.

31
00:01:34,200 --> 00:01:35,200
I'm asking you.

32
00:01:35,280 --> 00:01:36,480
Of course.

33
00:01:36,680 --> 00:01:38,600
You ask, I obey.

34
00:01:40,680 --> 00:01:41,720
We're good.

35
00:01:42,200 --> 00:01:43,200
Huh?

36
00:01:44,080 --> 00:01:46,400
We're good just like that?

37
00:01:46,600 --> 00:01:47,800
Yeah.

38
00:01:47,800 --> 00:01:49,720
Tawan asks, we obey.

39
00:01:58,240 --> 00:01:59,360
Are you okay?

40
00:02:35,600 --> 00:02:37,000
Thank you, Tawan.

41
00:02:38,760 --> 00:02:40,200
For saving me.

42
00:02:42,600 --> 00:02:44,200
You always protect me.

43
00:02:44,520 --> 00:02:46,400
It's like you're my bodyguard.

44
00:02:50,960 --> 00:02:52,480
Bodyguard?

45
00:02:54,240 --> 00:02:56,080
I'm expensive.

46
00:02:56,760 --> 00:02:58,040
Can you afford me?

47
00:03:04,120 --> 00:03:06,360
Can I ask you something?

48
00:03:09,440 --> 00:03:12,160
You love dancing, right?

49
00:03:16,960 --> 00:03:19,280
Yes, I love dancing.

50
00:03:20,680 --> 00:03:22,240
How did you know?

51
00:03:26,240 --> 00:03:27,440
Well,

52
00:03:27,920 --> 00:03:29,400
I saw you...

53
00:03:30,360 --> 00:03:32,800
when you mopped the club floor.

54
00:03:34,240 --> 00:03:35,640
You danced so hard

55
00:03:35,640 --> 00:03:36,640
the floor was clean.

56
00:03:36,720 --> 00:03:37,840
Huh?

57
00:03:43,800 --> 00:03:46,280
Tawan got my gift.

58
00:03:58,240 --> 00:03:59,880
You saw the whole thing?

59
00:04:01,720 --> 00:04:03,120
I saw the whole thing.

60
00:04:05,320 --> 00:04:06,840
I saw you were like...

61
00:04:12,760 --> 00:04:14,320
I'm gonna cry.

62
00:04:16,680 --> 00:04:17,880
You saw everything.

63
00:04:31,080 --> 00:04:33,920
Our school has an excellent dance club.

64
00:04:34,360 --> 00:04:36,920
I think you should join it.

65
00:04:38,440 --> 00:04:40,840
Kendo is too much for you.

66
00:04:41,760 --> 00:04:43,800
No, I like kendo.

67
00:04:44,640 --> 00:04:46,440
I like kendo.

68
00:04:49,040 --> 00:04:50,440
I even love it.

69
00:04:58,280 --> 00:05:00,240
You love kendo...

70
00:05:01,800 --> 00:05:03,200
more than you love dancing?

71
00:05:07,280 --> 00:05:08,640
I think...

72
00:05:10,360 --> 00:05:11,800
that's not true.

73
00:05:13,720 --> 00:05:15,040
Why not?

74
00:05:15,440 --> 00:05:17,920
Do I look that hopeless?

75
00:05:20,520 --> 00:05:21,520
Yes.

76
00:05:23,960 --> 00:05:27,560
Tawan, you're not very encouraging.

77
00:05:31,160 --> 00:05:32,600
Just trust me.

78
00:05:33,280 --> 00:05:34,840
Following your heart...

79
00:05:35,720 --> 00:05:37,000
is always better.

80
00:05:47,280 --> 00:05:48,400
But...

81
00:05:49,800 --> 00:05:51,960
if I'm not in the kendo club,

82
00:05:54,160 --> 00:05:56,640
I won't get to talk to you every day like this.

83
00:05:59,600 --> 00:06:00,720
Of course you will.

84
00:06:02,800 --> 00:06:04,960
You can say hi to me whenever you see me.

85
00:06:06,440 --> 00:06:07,760
Or...

86
00:06:10,120 --> 00:06:11,640
I train here every day.

87
00:06:13,520 --> 00:06:15,040
You can come if you want.

88
00:06:21,680 --> 00:06:22,840
It's a date.

89
00:06:26,600 --> 00:06:27,600
It's a date.

90
00:06:46,240 --> 00:06:50,880
♪ You are the moon in my heart ♪

91
00:06:50,880 --> 00:06:55,520
♪ You make everything ♪

92
00:06:55,520 --> 00:06:59,800
♪ More meaningful every day ♪

93
00:06:59,800 --> 00:07:04,280
♪ I wanna be your sun ♪

94
00:07:05,240 --> 00:07:09,040
♪ Please let me ♪

95
00:07:09,040 --> 00:07:15,120
♪ Be by your side and keep on loving you ♪

96
00:07:20,720 --> 00:07:24,120
♪ You bring light to the darkness ♪

97
00:07:24,120 --> 00:07:27,480
♪ You make me smile every day ♪

98
00:07:27,480 --> 00:07:34,000
♪ You make the lonely nights
More beautiful than they've ever been ♪

99
